Package edu.lafayette.bci Description

This package contains classes for processing BCI signals and sending/receiving signals to various BCI devices. The classes contained in the top-level package provide an implementation of an asynchronous BCI using the Emotiv EEG headset and the Parrot AR.Drone quadrotor.
Author:
Haley Garrison
